<h4>Accessing the Page Setup Options Box for Headers and Footers in Classic Microsoft Excel</h4>


<p>In Classic Microsoft Excel, you click on <strong>View</strong> in the toolbar at the top of the spreadsheet. From the drop down View Menu that appears, click on <strong>Header and Footer...</strong>. The Page Setup Options Box will open.</p>


