<div class="row">
<div class="twelve columns">
<h4>Custom Header Options Box in All Versions</h4>


<p>The <strong>Custom Header Options Box</strong> is the same for both the Header and the Footer.</p>

<p> Choose the placement of the text from <strong>Left section</strong>, <strong>Center section</strong>, and <strong>Right section</strong>, click in the section, and type in your information.</p>

<p>The icons allow you to format the information in the header and the footer and they also allow you to insert information like page number and date.</p>
 
<p>When you are finished with your selections, click OK.</p>


